data.description:
FOR SALE ONLY...NOT FOR RENT! This smart home has been LOVED and you don't want to miss it.  The elegant floorplan is great for entertaining with 2 living areas so there is plenty of space for everyone. Updated kitchen with Samsung stainless steel appliances including the refrigerator. Updated fireplace with stone. Bedrooms are of a very good size specially the Master which is HUGE. Master Bedroom has a his and hers closet. All bathrooms are completely remodeled.  Carpet replaced in 2021.  New light fixtures. Spotlights installed throughout the home.  Water heater is less than a year old.  HVAC system was replaced 2 years ago.  
Backyard has a 9.5 feet tall carport with concrete all throughout the backyard and side of the home making it perfect for extra parking.  Shed built in 2022.Total parking for 10 cars!!! Roof replaced in 2019.

Security system conveys with the home.

This is a real gem so don't miss it out!

ONLY FOR SALE...NOT FOR RENT!
